      <h1>【组图】13岁黑人少年被白人警察枪杀 涉事警察已被停职</h1>
      <span>时间：2016-09-17 06:54:36</span>
      <span>编辑：<a href="http://www.liuweispace.com/">六维空间</a>（<a href="http://m.liuweispace.com/">手机版</a>）</span>
     </div>
     <div class="b">
      <div style="text-align: center">
       <script async="" src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script> 
       <!-- 六维新闻网移动端文章页顶部 --> 
       <ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:inline-block;width:250px;height:250px" data-ad-client="ca-pub-1835474462644978" data-ad-slot="5028766429"></ins> 
       <script>
